      • searchSIF

        public boolean searchSIF(Model model,
                         OutputStream out)
        Searches the given model with the contained miners. Writes the textual result to the given output stream. Closes the stream at the end. Produces simplest version of SIF format.
        Parameters:
        model - model to search
        out - stream to write
        Returns:
        true if any output produced successfully
